    <ds:title>Legacy City-Parish Employee Annual Salaries</ds:title>
    <ds:category_or_snippet>Government</ds:category_or_snippet>
    <ds:description>***THIS DATASET IS NO LONGER UPDATED***   In November 2018, the City-Parish switched to a new payroll system. This dataset contains annual salaries through 2017. For data from 2018 onward, visit https://data.brla.gov/Government/City-Parish-Employee-Annual-Salaries/g9vh-zeiw   City-Parish employees' annual salaries and other payroll related information. Information is calculated after the last payroll is run for the year specified.</ds:description>
