    <ds:title>City-Parish Expense Budget</ds:title>
    <ds:category_or_snippet>Government</ds:category_or_snippet>
    <ds:description>The operating budget portion of Open Budget BR allows users to drill down into spending categories such as department-level and service-specific budgets. Browse the budget based on the fund or department and drill down to each spending category to better understand departmental expenses and revenue sources along with budgeted versus actual expenses incurred throughout the year, which can be viewed in greater detail at checkbook.brla.gov.</ds:description>
    <ds:tags>Budget, Expenses Operating, Open Budget BR, Open Budget</ds:tags>
    <ds:open_data_site>Open Data BR</ds:open_data_site>
